Ctrl+shift+down arrow		select all rows



Cell/Range Syntax {{{2

Range with tab name   ‘tab name’!A2:E
Absolute cell ref     $A$1

### Row/Column syntax
A:A     An entire column
2:2     entire row
B2:2    row starting with col.
B:D     contiguous cols.
B2:D    contiguous cols starting with row
2:5     contiguous rows
B2:5    contiguous rows starting with col.

